# Code of Conduct

## Our Pledge

We pledge to make participation in {{ repoName }} a harassment-free experience for everyone.

## Our Standards

**Positive behavior includes:**
- Using welcoming and inclusive language
- Being respectful of differing viewpoints
- Gracefully accepting constructive criticism
- Focusing on what is best for the community

**Unacceptable behavior includes:**
- Harassment of any kind
- Discriminatory jokes and language
- Personal or political attacks
- Publishing others' private information

## Enforcement

Instances of abusive behavior may be reported to:
{% if maintainerEmail %}{{ maintainerEmail }}{% else %}the project maintainers{% endif %}.

All complaints will be reviewed and investigated promptly and fairly.

## Attribution

This Code of Conduct is adapted from the [Contributor Covenant](https://www.contributor-covenant.org/), version 2.1.
